{"text_id":245876,"tokens":["The"," UL","Xs"," (","Ultra","-","L","uminous"," X","-","ray"," Sources",")"," population"," in"," nearby"," galaxies"," is"," characterized"," by"," extreme"," lum","ino","sities",","," exceeding"," tens"," of"," thousands"," of"," times"," the"," Edd","ington"," limit"," for"," stellar","-","mass"," black"," holes","."," The"," estimation"," of"," these"," lum","ino","sities",","," however",","," relies"," heavily"," on"," the"," chosen"," spectral"," model",","," which"," can"," introduce"," systematic"," uncertainties","."," We"," attempt"," to"," address"," this"," issue"," by"," investigating"," the"," dependence"," of"," the"," estimated"," lum","ino","sities"," of"," UL","Xs"," on"," different"," spectral"," models",","," using"," a"," comprehensive"," sample"," of"," ","2","1"," UL","Xs","."," Our"," key"," idea"," is"," to"," utilize"," the"," X","-","ray"," spectral"," properties"," of"," UL","Xs"," to"," identify"," the"," most"," suitable"," spectral"," models"," for"," their"," luminosity"," estimation","."," We"," achieve"," this"," by"," combining"," X","-","ray"," spectroscopy"," and"," photo","metry"," to"," constrain"," the"," models","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," fitting"," a"," variety"," of"," spectral"," models",","," including"," thermal"," plasma"," models",","," disk","-","based"," models",","," and"," alternative"," models",","," to"," the"," observed"," X","-","ray"," spectra"," of"," UL","Xs","."," Our"," research"," aims"," to"," improve"," the"," accuracy"," of"," UL","X"," luminosity"," estimates",","," which"," is"," crucial"," for"," understanding"," their"," nature",","," evolution",","," and"," role"," in"," galaxy"," evolution","."," By"," exploring"," the"," dependence"," of"," estimated"," lum","ino","sities"," on"," spectral"," models",","," we"," hope"," to"," provide"," a"," robust"," foundation"," for"," future"," studies"," of"," UL","Xs","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b",